      "content": "idk im just really hesitant about taking more. if i take them every other day like i suggested, it's basically still the same amount of medicine over time but without the constant dose, right? it seems way more logical than just finishing the whole thing when the skin is already perfect. wouldn't that still kill off whatever is left without the extra side effects?",
